@mohsen1 we/you should be overriding the parent values according to spec at https://github.com/swagger-api/swagger-spec/blob/master/versions/2.0.md#operationObject . The security field states "This definition overrides any declared top-level security. To remove a top-level security declaration, an empty array can be used."
. The spec indicates that operation level security arrays should override top-level security arrays. The top-level security should seemingly only be extended when the operation level does not define a security array.
